profile:
Zhu Yuanzhang (Chinese: 朱元璋）  (21 October 1328 – 24 June 1398)。
Era name:  The Hongwu Emperor. (洪武)
Courtesy name Guorui (simplified Chinese: 国瑞; traditional Chinese: 國瑞), was the founding emperor of the Ming dynasty, 
Reigning from 1368 to 1398.
Posthumous name: Emperor Gāo (高皇帝)
Temple name: Tàizǔ (太祖)

Zhu Biao (simplified Chinese: 朱标; traditional Chinese: 朱標; 10 October 1355 – 17 May 1392).
he was the Hongwu Emperor's eldest son and crown prince of the Ming dynasty.
Crown Prince Yiwen (懿文太子) by his father and Xingzong (興宗), Emperor Xiaokang (孝康皇帝) by his son.

Zhu Di (Chinese: 朱棣; 2 May 1360 – 12 August 1424), Zhu Di was the fourth son of the Hongwu Emperor,He was originally enfeoffed as the Prince of Yan (燕王) in May 1370.
Reign: 17 July 1402 – 12 August 1424
Era name: Yǒnglè 永樂
Posthumous name: Emperor Wén 文皇帝
Temple name: Tàizōng 太宗 and Chéngzǔ 成祖

Zhu Yunwen (朱允炆).  (5 December 1377 – 13 July 1402) was the second Emperor of the Ming dynasty,
Era name: Jianwen Emperor
Reign: 30 June 1398 – 13 July 1402
Posthumous name: Emperor Ràng 讓皇帝
Temple name:  Huìzōng 惠宗

Zhu Gaochi was born on 16 August 1378 and was educated by prominent Confucian tutors. He often acted as regent in Nanjing or Beijing during his father's northern military campaigns.
Era name: Hongxi (洪熙) 1425
Reign: 7 September 1424 – 29 May 1425
Posthumous name: Emperor Zhāo 昭皇帝

Zhu Zhanji (朱瞻基), was the fifth Emperor of the Ming dynasty,
Era name:Xuande Emperor (宣德)
reigned from 1425 to 1435
Posthumous name: Emperor Zhāng 章皇帝
Temple name  Xuānzōng 宣宗

Zhu Qizhen (Chinese: 朱祁鎮; 29 November 1427 – 23 February 1464) 
Era name: Zhèngtǒng 正統 Tiānshùn天順
Reign: 7 February 1435 – 1 September 1449 / 11 February 1457 – 23 February 1464
Posthumous name	 Emperor Ruì 睿皇帝
Temple name[ Yīngzōng 英宗

Zhu Qiyu (21 September 1428 – 14 March 1457),was the seventh Emperor of the Ming dynasty The second son of the Xuande Emperor,
Era name: Jǐngtài 景泰
Reign 22 September 1449 – 14 March 1457
Posthumous name:Emperor Jǐng 景皇帝
Temple name:Dàizōng 代宗

Zhu Jianshen 朱見深 9 December 1447 – 9 September 1487),was the ninth Emperor of the Ming dynasty
Era name Chénghuà 成化
reigned from 1464 to 1487.
Posthumous name:	Emperor Chún 純皇帝
Temple name Xiànzōng憲宗
